@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="row">

    <p class="lead"><b>Welcome to Microsoft Azure Stream Analytics TollApp Sample</b>
    </p>
    <p>The TollApp Sample allows you to visualize entry and exit data when a vehicle passes through a toll booth.</p>
    <p>
        For scenario information, see <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/stream-analytics/stream-analytics-build-an-iot-solution-using-stream-analytics">https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/stream-analytics/stream-analytics-build-an-iot-solution-using-stream-analytics</a>
    </p>

    <p>For tutorials that reference these samples, see <a href="http://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/documentation/services/stream-analytics/">http://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/documentation/services/stream-analytics/</a>
    </p>

    <p>For more information about the Stream Analytics service, see <a href="http://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/stream-analytics">http://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/stream-analytics</a>
    </p>

    <br/>
    Verify that the Azure Stream Analytics TollApp deployment was successful
    <br/>Login into Microsoft Azure portal
    <br/>Go to Resource Groups
    <br/>Select the Resource Group name used during deployment
    <br/>Verify that the following services are listed
    <ul>
        <li>One Cosmos DB</li>
        <li>Two Azure Streaming Analytics Jobs</li>
        <li>One Azure Storage Account</li>
        <li>One Azure Event Hubs</li>
        <li>Two Web Apps</li>
    </ul>

    <br/>
    <p>The TollApp web app contains a Web Job that can be started and stopped to control the consumption used by Azure Event Hubs. Follow these steps to either Start or Stop the Web Job:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Login into Microsoft Azure portal</li>
        <li>Go to Resource Groups</li>
        <li>Select the Web App</li>
        <li>From the configuration blade, select WebJobs</li>
        <li>Select the TollApp WebJob and click Start/Stop depending on the status</li>
    </ol>


    <br/> Subscription Id: @Model.SubscriptionId
    <br/> Resource Group Name: @Model.ResourceGroup
    <br/> Job Name: @Model.JobName
    <br/> Deployment Logs: <a href="@Model.DeploymentLogLink">@Model.DeploymentLogLink</a>

</div>